  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Legal notice</h1>
  <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <p>
      <strong>Publisher:</strong> this site is published by Alexis Fiska under a freelance/portage
      arrangement.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Address:</strong> No postal address is published because the activity is performed
      remotely and on site at clients. For correspondence please use the contact form or the email
      address provided.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Legal status:</strong> independent contractor under a portage contract. No SIREN number.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Hosting:</strong> the site is hosted on GitHub Pages.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Intellectual property:</strong> all content (texts, images, code) is the property of the
      publisher unless otherwise stated. Any reproduction or use without permission is prohibited.
    </p>
    <p>
      For any questions regarding the legal notice please contact us via the contact form.
    </p>
  </div>
